  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    iiVScriptable
    iiVScriptable defines routines to allow setting the slice of data displayed by a component.

    Class to handle parsing iiV scripts.
    CNUScriptObjects

    A JFC/Swing based console for the BeanShell desktop.
    iiVBshJConsole.BlockingPipedInputStream
    The overridden read method in this class will not throw "Broken pipe" IOExceptions; It will simply wait for new writers and data.
